dc_title_s: Colton's map of the world: on Mercator's projection.
dc_description_s: No. VIII-IX in Colton, G.W. Atlas of the world. v.2. 1856. Shows routes of various explorers. 1 map: col.; 41 x 63 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
